about_the_job:
Ringan is an innovative and fast-growing non-bank lending company, dedicated to provide financial services to micro and small business owners. As part of our expansion, we are seeking an experienced Backend-Java Developer to join our IT team. The ideal candidate should have a strong background and exposure in using various open source frameworks. As the Java Developer, you will be responsible in writing system architecture design-related and design document, to test-optimize and maintain the project to ensure its stability and reliability.

Key Responsibilities:
Responsible for backend or API development;
Ensure good code quality and it functionality performance approval system requirements and optimization;
Work closely with the Mobile Engineer team and Frontend Engineer team to ensure the smooth progress of the project;
Eager to learn new technologies and tools to improve tech team capabilities;
Test, optimize and maintain the project to ensure its stability and reliability.
Receive the handover and participate in the transition for API or Backend development from HQ


Qualifications:
1. 3 years minimum experience in software development;
2. Diploma Degree and above in computer related major, Indonesian;
3. Proficient in Java, Spring, SQL Databases (MySQL & Postgres) and have understanding about Cache, and Queue, and Load Balancing;
4. Familiar with the Backend CI/CD, API Management, and Design Patterns
